they are hence sosmat demanded aswell as any otherspecia of gold therefore
will not loose one pennieby thm 3 sake notice what you say of the
kersies, & can not afford to give more ƒ21: yett if they beworth ƒ21:10
I'll allowitt, butt more not neither should g desire above 6 or 8 peeces for

send them butt not above 10 a 12 prs & lett mee have them socheap as
possibly you can afferd, for there is litte or nothing to be gott by here
trade bengentreamly bad. so I make use of yd word domeer

last acctt sent you there were butt 17 p. of serges resting & the ballance of

Sr. in answer to yd of 11 & 18: pass I do much want the bayes in ordered, prill
not question, butt that bj yd care they begott aboard of smith or him that say:
leth first from hull, fo roterwise itt would be great preiudice to our sall
please also to informe mee pr. vere first how all sorts of wollen mans facttdd
rill now in the north, for though wee have not had that sale, which wee could
have exspected, yett shall wanh about 6o cloathes & 200 bayes fowards
spring & & never louf to be behinde hand in time of demanditherefore informe
yd self well & advise mee to give orders & directions accordingly yett before
proceeding, wee must go on with good understanding of eacheither, & you must
not draw on mee as oof late you have don other wise I can not continew for
Iam altoghether against that kinde of dealing, for our trade must bedriven
with some stock, which can not be imployed other wages, butt there ontmust
be continually paye what wee demand & that wee cando, butt for you to be straightned
on other acctt & then to charge the cloth acctt. for itt, can be tonether yd or mme
conveniency or proffitt, & doubt & shall not be able to pay the bills due ingam
next, therefore you will do well to advise mee whom to draw up on in case
of yntraights & (haveing so much dagly now to pay, hope you will nott
refuse to accept a £100:- tom Georgo bale for yd brother desee seis esfate
which I shall do p. next if I can not avoid itt other wise pray endeavour
to send an accopt of the bayes norw shipt as also an acctt of charges
in then my acctt curitt for wee usually ballance once a yeare, which is ul
xb. now instant when god willing you will have all the acctt till
